{
  "logNo": "224304064028",
  "title": "자율신경실조증에 의한 위장 증상 및 관리",
  "addDate": "2026. 6. 2.",
  "categoryNo": "38",
  "parentCategoryNo": "",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=224304064028",
  "blocks": [],
  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-aae08011-fda9-4e6a-8cc5-8e05de40325a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f3ad5371-0876-408c-830e-1fb42e3a7d42\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-15b1c40f-09ff-4d8c-91ab-f38f88283dad\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4294a391-516b-4cf2-89bb-19280c84d72b\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2d727079-f850-4d9f-9801-0e3f39c77435\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c9c68b2c-01ad-4080-b67e-6417caee21b6\">자율신경계는 위장관의 운동, 분비, 혈류를 조절하는 핵심 네트워크입니다. 특히 장신경계(Enteric Nervous System)와 긴밀하게 연결되어 있어, 자율신경의 균형이 깨지면(교감신경 항진 및 부교감신경 저하) 소화기 전반에 걸쳐 다양한 기능 이상이 발생하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0f8467fa-8e17-4dd9-97b9-597d0238bb75\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1c9260ca-780f-47fd-a7aa-274bfefcad71\">임상에서 자주 접하게 되는 자율신경 이상으로 인한 위장관 증상과 병태생리, 그리고 관리법을 아래와 같이 정리합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1e8841d2-6adf-4943-9249-d278f9b9fa14\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b022a710-fc28-44ab-be90-d89e074d2312\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-f3ad5371-0876-408c-830e-1fb42e3a7d42\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6693d82e-db7c-4921-9c57-b71a2400783a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6693d82e-db7c-4921-9c57-b71a2400783a\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8e142c181d91735d.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2816\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1536\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"8861844\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8e142c181d91735d.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8e142c181d91735d.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"272\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-6693d82e-db7c-4921-9c57-b71a2400783a\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\", \"fileSize\": \"8861844\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-803175a1-8153-4ed2-816e-dcc2cfcd75d8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-031a0b60-2cfd-49a1-9413-39927cfe1104\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5e957787-03c3-4ef6-8efe-8153a3c7cd23\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b4adc60a-f10c-4fcb-ad8b-c12e390b4820\"><span style=\"color:#003366;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-add1a384-ef64-4c98-b878-733f85685dae\"><b>1. 자율신경 이상 시 나타나는 위장관 증상</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1e626662-4bed-4faa-b66b-76df7cf7ba8d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a5bff287-371b-443b-9521-afa6e770912a\">위장관은 교감신경이 억제성(운동 저하, 괄약근 수축), 부교감신경(미주신경)이 흥분성(운동 촉진, 분비 증가)으로 작용합니다. 이 균형이 무너지면 부위에 따라 다음과 같은 증상이 나타납니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-803175a1-8153-4ed2-816e-dcc2cfcd75d8\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bf7a1ceb-2d0f-471d-8e67-6384c3806ea0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-bf7a1ceb-2d0f-471d-8e67-6384c3806ea0\", \"src\" : \"https://nuhsplus.edu.sg/images/default-source/default-album/chronic-bowel-issue.png?sfvrsn=c9e5c265_1\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1200\", \"originalHeight\" : \"550\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"0\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://nuhsplus.edu.sg/images/default-source/default-album/chronic-bowel-issue.png?sfvrsn=c9e5c265_1\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-bf7a1ceb-2d0f-471d-8e67-6384c3806ea0\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\", \"fileSize\": \"0\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7483b91c-fdfb-4aaa-8026-b6c67b5f8e74\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1d461353-cb1c-4a23-8d03-d3c08aa953a8\"><span style=\"color:#006699;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8619de57-a1db-4462-857a-22e8d2baed88\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dfa3196e-d932-46bd-adc6-47ca4ae1a023\"><span style=\"color:#006699;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b347eca5-aa94-4c98-a23a-ddfd082e259c\"><b>상부 위장관 증상</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dce7133a-b941-4e75-a93d-a08d95feee30\"><span style=\"color:#006699;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d23954e8-72d5-43f9-968c-df5c9fd8e829\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ed99ec5b-7b41-40fc-80af-f6bc8b59a63f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c3758f04-11b0-472e-8b7b-3596ed01d6fa\">·   위마비(Gastroparesis): </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f35f12b7-fb86-4efa-b66e-04bb3268d12f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ff38fe04-1ccb-47db-b8fc-4c51074ef25a\">미주신경 손상이나 기능 저하로 위 배출 시간이 지연됩니다. 조기 포만감, 식후 팽만감, 구역, 구토가 특징입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-efd5a828-4ce8-48e8-aa21-18df2c718225\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3752a345-c8d1-4ff1-a5ad-92e0e97bba03\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b7df74d4-85bc-4afe-9db8-a0f6e62e037e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6f9e22d4-de01-4e9c-8e46-ad9359ca3dde\">·    연하 곤란 및 역류: </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ee3e5432-03ad-492b-91af-732ee8f155c0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-09857e93-f2b3-4051-ab9a-767bdcb55618\">식도 괄약근의 조절 이상으로 삼킴이 어렵거나 위산 역류(GERD)가 악화될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-63a07dc9-2d0f-4970-9141-1e9eb343ff9c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e70df7a2-68e1-49ec-9646-b145a7c1000f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c05ef768-e8fb-4f8f-aad5-ba951595ab88\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-40b76f8e-bada-4bd8-b8dd-5ae74ff882be\">·    기능성 소화불량: </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5132214b-cb34-4428-96f7-916f5a066cd3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-785aaf3a-759a-487c-911f-bb19b4e82f53\">기질적 병변 없이 명치 부위의 통증이나 쓰림이 발생합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b4f42e94-c927-4c43-b935-4900a76da7ea\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b405820d-112f-471b-ab0a-b26a82e51a34\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-7483b91c-fdfb-4aaa-8026-b6c67b5f8e74\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-35cafd8b-6445-4e0a-b6f1-a40d93d9422d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:400px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-35cafd8b-6445-4e0a-b6f1-a40d93d9422d\", \"src\" : \"https://drossmancare.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/4683197_s.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"400\", \"originalHeight\" : \"300\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"0\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://drossmancare.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/4683197_s.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-35cafd8b-6445-4e0a-b6f1-a40d93d9422d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\", \"fileSize\": \"0\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b681f5a7-3ee6-4502-8510-be706237f085\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-85609468-035f-4a95-bf3e-78ecf4e8fdff\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-60ffd81d-2f91-4c2c-a3c9-4d484155ea88\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4c2bdcf8-f027-4d3e-822d-dc707a66f3cc\"><span style=\"color:#006699;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d4d341c8-76f3-4bfa-9feb-e56cc8489312\"><b>하부 위장관 증상</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-51546506-444c-432b-807b-42911c7bd6fc\"><span style=\"color:#006699;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9a9601f1-f8b6-4df2-a5c8-e8718470d064\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eda42676-4d1a-4ae9-acc8-3e1e84fce28f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2f79ffea-5b43-4498-a1e6-0314401489d7\">·    만성 변비 또는 설사: </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3cb66998-eff9-43db-b79c-464b7c71f538\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-56a273d6-7e62-4837-bb6a-914e3a30bb1e\">장 연동운동이 심하게 저하되면 변비가, 반대로 흡수 기능이 떨어지거나 장내 세균총이 변화하면 설사가 발생합니다. 교대로 나타나는 과민성 대장 증후군(IBS) 형태를 보이기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6e4549c7-d4dc-4994-95fd-69668a6ecdfb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-75b7a806-c5ff-48d5-90b9-74bb682ad2e7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3e549e78-902b-4c67-8019-3eda9af4debe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-33cfc33d-c997-48fc-848a-cc9cc2791b0d\">·    담즙 및 췌장액 분비 저하: </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a180f793-ab16-4969-87f5-17576a95a56c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b751ad40-fc98-4266-b621-88234b38237c\">소화 효소 분비가 원활하지 않아 지방변이나 소화불량이 동반될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-985dbaf6-1f04-4930-8eee-843dbac98a0c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bf6034d5-f1fc-4baf-959d-285b261e8cc8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-b681f5a7-3ee6-4502-8510-be706237f085\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a983282b-7a8d-4d59-9c16-81350da7debe\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:273px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a983282b-7a8d-4d59-9c16-81350da7debe\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7454868f70b3d06d.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"273\", \"originalHeight\" : \"185\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"6503\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7454868f70b3d06d.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7454868f70b3d06d.jpg\" data-width=\"273\" data-height=\"185\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-a983282b-7a8d-4d59-9c16-81350da7debe\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\", \"fileSize\": \"6503\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e4c78e54-7516-463c-8000-c7a804c8aeaa\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text